due to the energy reserve releases in the comm ercial portfolio in
2018, partially offset by the impact of recoveries recorded in
connection with sales of previously charged-of f non-core
consumer real estate loans. For more information on the
provision for credit losses, see Provision for Credit Losses  on
page 68.
