delinquencies, nonperfo rming status, charge-of fs and troubled
debt restructurings (TDRs) for the consumer portfolio, see Note 1
– Summary of Significant Accounting Principle s and Note 5 –
Outstanding Loans and Leases  to the Consolidated Financial
Statements .
